      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s still in really great shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and drives like a dream\u2014perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend adventures. It\u2019s super clean, runs smoothly, and is totally ready for its next chapter. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 28900.0,
