    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 987.2-generation Porsche Cayman S is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the robust 3.4L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six engine. Delivering 320 hp with a linear power band, this mid-engine platform offers a neutral handling balance and an exceptional polar moment of inertia. The longitudinal 6-speed manual transaxle provides tactile, short-throw shifts, paired with a chassis featuring Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for optimized damping. Mechanically sound with a clean DME overrev report, it benefits from a recent high-pressure fuel pump replacement and a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. The hydraulic steering rack remains communicative, providing the raw feedback modern EPAS systems lack. A high-performance driver\u2019s car ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 32500.0,
