    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained premium sedan that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and performance. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like luster, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the leading edge of the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical of a well-loved daily driver. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the charcoal leather seats remain supple with only light creasing on the driver's side bolster, and the interior has never been smoked in. Every electronic feature, from the premium surround-sound system to the dual-zone climate control and heated steering wheel, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound. The turbocharged engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. I have maintained a comprehensive folder of service records, including a recent oil change and a fresh brake pad replacement. The tires are high-quality all-seasons with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a solid, reliable, and honest vehicle ready for its next owner.",
